1434
01:30:16,959 --> 01:30:18,756
- Je...
- Assis !

1435
01:30:18,920 --> 01:30:20,831
- Je voudrais...
- La ferme !

1436
01:30:21,760 --> 01:30:24,433
Tiens-toi tranquille
