1437
01:30:24,600 --> 01:30:26,591
Regardez...

1438
01:30:31,039 --> 01:30:32,108
Hanaya Hosaburo ?

1439
01:30:32,479 --> 01:30:35,357
Le 15 août 1945...

1440
01:30:35,519 --> 01:30:37,430
signé : Zhao Zixuan, Ma Dasan,

1441
01:30:37,600 --> 01:30:40,637
Hanaya Hosaburo,Dong Hanchen.

1442
01:30:49,999 --> 01:30:51,478
Hanaya...

1443
01:30:52,159 --> 01:30:55,390
au lieu de t'excuser,
